{"tid":1550710,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對比左膠同藍絲分別","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T10:51:47.000Z","uid":173326,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"737cfa10921e1bb1c5e1b35f0c4b89e3fd087607","tid":1550710,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:15:21.000Z","msg":"藍絲：<br />\n1. 支持黑警，強國人圍爐支持<br />\n2. 狗損少少就嗌哂可憐<br />\n3. 邊個掙扎就係暴徒<br />\n4. 幫狗捉抗爭者<br />\n5. 黑警亂打無辜路人就扮睇唔到，跟住入抗爭者數<br />\n<br />\n左膠：<br />\n1. 保護黑警，攞愛與和平道德光環<br />\n2. 狗損少少就話俾位入破壞運動<br />\n3. 邊個還手就係鬼<br />\n4. 幫狗擋想還手/救人嘅抗爭者<br />\n5. 黑警亂打無辜路人都唔會阻止，只會口頭鬧黑警"},{"pid":"b69e88fa17c1805dbc767724b783b7651e5ab5d9","tid":1550710,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21fc1515b90bceac00463967db0f2b369cfdd293","tid":1550710,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5TuAzY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5TuAzY.jpg&h=486c9df7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28756c582549859c20ee62f96f577be938e0122d","tid":1550710,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:16:40.000Z","msg":"而且個個都廢老甘地上身咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d507b52f6337ad090285cc41e794ab93d732d83","tid":1550710,"uid":258592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:16:41.000Z","msg":"和理非不等同左膠<br />\n<br />\n左膠同偽中立撚藍絲一撚樣"},{"pid":"6593256e7dd41da240d08c51ad996b2b2f49b5ed","tid":1550710,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:17:08.000Z","msg":"左膠比藍絲更低賤<br />\n左膠扮自己人但就陰d陰d背後插你一刀，搞到自己人被人拉<br />\n藍絲起碼擺到明係敵人"},{"pid":"42378972ac3d1fd4d74b9eb5f224b82604aa8910","tid":1550710,"uid":226413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:17:48.000Z","msg":"左膠係會出手阻止人<br />\n和理非唔會，自己唔打就ok"},{"pid":"0876f452bca3d6020a12c84856a1e23b23639afe","tid":1550710,"uid":20809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"一係就推隻左膠俾藍絲打<br />\n<br />\n一係就打隻左膠先"},{"pid":"874ea2b73613ccfad23b310039a1728585dde8d0","tid":1550710,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d507b52f6337ad090285cc41e794ab93d732d83","tid":1550710,"uid":258592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:16:41.000Z","msg":"和理非不等同左膠<br />\n<br />\n左膠同偽中立撚藍絲一撚樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:18:19.000Z","msg":"和理非只係行動上唔會出手，但內心會支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左膠真係單純地相信愛與和平穿透坦克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982b6c45ec7914a4a58b96c0c627b22b4c56f4c8","tid":1550710,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"874ea2b73613ccfad23b310039a1728585dde8d0","tid":1550710,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d507b52f6337ad090285cc41e794ab93d732d83","tid":1550710,"uid":258592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:16:41.000Z","msg":"和理非不等同左膠<br />\n<br />\n左膠同偽中立撚藍絲一撚樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:18:19.000Z","msg":"和理非只係行動上唔會出手，但內心會支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左膠真係單純地相信愛與和平穿透坦克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"大把和理非識出手開遮<br />\n左膠仆街死啦"},{"pid":"273254dc11474ba084758f5e68e364157fbdf9ea","tid":1550710,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:19:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要記住左膠就係藍絲</span></span>"},{"pid":"28eb349692dd26a97286a6457bc4b10913b8af1c","tid":1550710,"uid":40628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:20:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要說 「 左膠 」<br />\n<br />\n試着說 「 藍絲臥底 」</span>"},{"pid":"3854133013019d16d3c6d9524653a47e02f81e83","tid":1550710,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:20:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5227402aa2bdc019448dac14d7ba40dea59d3b02","tid":1550710,"uid":254558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:20:49.000Z","msg":"【修訂版】元朗9.9七點三有人鏈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dQmteS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dQmteS</a>"},{"pid":"d821bd73ca996b65b87d1bc217576350d3ba1586","tid":1550710,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:20:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6f2040565973ea36df1c8e61edff1ffc5e3eaa03","tid":1550710,"uid":55144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:21:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"10ce9aaae1376fe05be744a0ecdffa49d3ddd2bb","tid":1550710,"uid":265902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"737cfa10921e1bb1c5e1b35f0c4b89e3fd087607","tid":1550710,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:15:21.000Z","msg":"藍絲：<br />\n1. 支持黑警，強國人圍爐支持<br />\n2. 狗損少少就嗌哂可憐<br />\n3. 邊個掙扎就係暴徒<br />\n4. 幫狗捉抗爭者<br />\n5. 黑警亂打無辜路人就扮睇唔到，跟住入抗爭者數<br />\n<br />\n左膠：<br />\n1. 保護黑警，攞愛與和平道德光環<br />\n2. 狗損少少就話俾位入破壞運動<br />\n3. 邊個還手就係鬼<br />\n4. 幫狗擋想還手/救人嘅抗爭者<br />\n5. 黑警亂打無辜路人都唔會阻止，只會口頭鬧黑警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"好的不割席呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n但不包括阻膠，因為佢地喺敵人，喺累死我地手足嘅鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a0c25befa98cc2bfe4ac46d12df8438cb46cf0","tid":1550710,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:21:53.000Z","msg":"惻隱之心害死人"},{"pid":"4c52ad880b8f8d1cd0855c7b867888a28630f705","tid":1550710,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:08.000Z","msg":"唔該呢樣野真係要做文宣，同埋全世界要長期帶直遮見落單狗就勒佢落地炮製佢"},{"pid":"4b925b3e3336a0342be6e4dd97c88b9064d9b7fd","tid":1550710,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"但黑警打你個陣無憐憫過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f05ad1f9cc917843f1e59a87a23e10509a8807","tid":1550710,"uid":46148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"左膠係藍絲同黨 <br />\n完"},{"pid":"f79eac17b83766fab55e9f2d57f515a5db11c27e","tid":1550710,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07